---
---

<section id="motivation">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why Freeshard?</h2>
    <p class="section-description">
      Built by developers, for developers
    </p>
    <div class="motivation-content">
      <div class="motivation-text">
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <p>
          We built Freeshard because we were frustrated with the complexity and cost of existing cloud platforms. 
          As developers ourselves, we knew there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Freeshard was designed from the ground up to be simple, transparent, and developer-friendly. 
          No hidden fees, no complex pricing tiers, and no vendor lock-in.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a solo developer building a side project or a large enterprise deploying mission-critical 
          applications, Freeshard scales with you every step of the way.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="motivation-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">99.99%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Uptime SLA</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">10k+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">50ms</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Response Time</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Support</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .motivation-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .motivation-text h3 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .motivation-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .motivation-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .motivation-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .motivation-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
